<h1>Privacy Policy</h1>

<p><em>Last updated: March 2026</em></p>

<h2>What We Collect</h2>

<p>
  When you log in, your call sign and basic profile info are stored on our servers.
  Your net activity (monitoring, chat messages, reactions, and favorites) is stored
  on our servers and visible to other logged-in users for the duration of the net.
</p>

<p>
  If you enable push notifications in the mobile app, your device token is stored
  on our servers.
</p>

<p>
  For each net, we store check-ins and chat messages only for the duration of the net
  itself. Once the net ends, that information is deleted from our database.
</p>

<p>
  Check-in location data (grid square, city, state, coordinates) originates from
  NetLogger and is displayed as-is. We do not collect your device's GPS location.
</p>

<p>
  If you use the EchoLink feature, the app will request access to your device's
  microphone. The microphone is used solely to transmit audio while you are actively
  pressing the push-to-talk button. Audio is streamed directly to the EchoLink proxy
  server and is not recorded, stored, or processed by RagChew.
</p>

<p>
  The App uses <a href="https://policies.google.com/privacy">Google Firebase Analytics</a>
  to collect anonymized usage data. No call sign or credentials are included in analytics events.
</p>

<h2>Third-Party Services</h2>

<ul>
  <li><strong>Google Firebase</strong> — push notifications and analytics. <a href="https://policies.google.com/privacy">Privacy Policy</a>.</li>
  <li><strong>Pusher</strong> — real-time net updates. <a href="https://pusher.com/legal/privacy-policy/">Privacy Policy</a>.</li>
  <li><strong>Honeybadger</strong> — error monitoring. Error reports may include your user ID and call sign. <a href="https://www.honeybadger.io/privacy/">Privacy Policy</a>.</li>
  <li><strong>NetLogger</strong> — RagChew mirrors net data from NetLogger. We are not affiliated with NetLogger.org.</li>
  <li><strong>EchoLink</strong> — if you use the EchoLink feature, your EchoLink credentials and audio are transmitted to EchoLink proxy servers operated by EchoLink. We are not affiliated with EchoLink. <a href="https://www.echolink.org/privacy.htm">Privacy Policy</a>.</li>
</ul>

<h2>Account Deletion</h2>

<p>
  You may delete your account at any time using this URL (if logged in): <a href="/user/delete">/user/delete</a>
</p>

<h2>Contact</h2>

<p>
  Questions? Contact us at <a href="mailto:support@ragchew.app">support@ragchew.app</a>.
</p>
